squidpony.squidmath

Class MummyNoise

  • java.lang.Object
    • squidpony.squidmath.MummyNoise
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Noise.Noise2D, Noise.Noise3D, Noise.Noise4D, Noise.Noise6D

    @Beta
public class MummyNoise
extends Object
implements Noise.Noise2D, Noise.Noise3D, Noise.Noise4D, Noise.Noise6D
    A different kind of noise that has spotted and striped areas, like a tabby cat. Highly experimental and expected to change; currently has significant linear artifacts, though they do wiggle. Created by Tommy Ettinger on 9/2/2017.

      • determine

        public static long determine(long state)
        The same as DiverRNG.determine(long), except this assumes state has already been multiplied by 0x632BE59BD9B4E019L.
        Parameters:
        state - a long that should change in increments of 0x632BE59BD9B4E019L
        Returns:
        a pseudo-random permutation of state
